Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings your esteemed presence here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:38.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(131,280)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1850,2200)}Chén Guī
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Placing troops along Beichang district...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...the horses are eager for another "radish" after those two cities...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This poses a military threat we must stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.98,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(113,340)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1200,1500)}Lǚ Bù\NStyled- Fèngxiān
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you speak thus?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying, my lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long ago, when Lord Yuán sent you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,gold, silk, and lots of rice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,his true purpose was to bribe you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to eliminate Liú Xuándé!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, sir, shot an arrow through your\Nhalberd to shut the issue down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now today, he has come to propose a marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Intending to..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to take your daughter hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, he will come to attack Liú Bèi\Nand snatch Xiǎopèi from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If Xiǎopèi falls, then Xú province will...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Be in peril?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}This is known as the 'isolating a family' strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}'Isolating a family'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, Yuán Shù may come to ask for grain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or he will ask us for troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to accept,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he will surely exhaust your supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to decline,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be trouble towards your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be abandoning your\Nrelatives and inviting hostilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, I was told that Yuán Shù\Nhad intentions to declare himself emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an act leading to rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ally with him and he rebels,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then you, General, will be a relative of a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How could the world tolerate you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chén Gōng misled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Order Zhāng Liáo and a few men to chase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I must get my daughter back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhāng! You must chase my daughter and get her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Fēi, you oaf!\NLeave the horses you've stolen behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,General, the horses we bought were stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this?! The audacity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out he is Liú Bèi's brother, Zhāng Fēi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Large-eyed brute!\NHe's terrorized me too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Muster the troops! Muster the troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Fēi, I will fight you and\Nsee who's superior and inferior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.06,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(564,345)\fade(255,0,255,0,540,1455,1740)}Liú Bèi\NStyled - Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother, why did you lead your troops here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot an arrow through my halberd, saving you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but now you steal my horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we needed horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent people to purchase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I ever steal your horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You told your brother Zhāng Fēi to be a bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The horses from Shāndōng were coming\Nwhen he stole them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you dare deny reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.22,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(586,340)\fade(255,0,255,0,415,2000,2340)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled - Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole your horses! \NWhat're you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Large-eyed brute!\NYou've repeatedly abused me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I steal your horses, you're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you stole my brother's land,\Nhow did we feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Sound the retreat signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have returned all of the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:50.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(134,379)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5050,5340)}Sūn Qián\NStyled - Gōngyòu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But that Lǚ Bù...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard of three fathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(97,348)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1650,1980)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled - Yúnchǎng
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, Lǚ Bù's attack on us is\Nso intense! Xiǎopèi won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo despises Lǚ Bù the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though you, My Lord,\Nhave already returned the horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù still won't withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As I see it, it would be better to abandon Xiǎopèi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,go to Xǔdū, and seek shelter under Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We could ask for troops and\Ndefeat Lǚ Bù again in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why need aid from Cáo Cāo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I'm not scared of that Lǚ Bù!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You always end up causing unneeded trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, you can't over drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother, are you against me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm drinking isn't wine, it's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We go under Lǚ Bù, then go under Cáo Cāo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be able to endure it, but I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'll lead the vanguard and break the siege?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The sin is mine. I will give my life to get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My beloved brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We all know that you are a just and frank man,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and that you hate erratic and\Ndishonest people like Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think I feel the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But when a true man acts in troubled times,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they must be open-minded and upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the face of adversity, we must bow to others and wait for the right time to rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't oppose our fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At the third watch, we'll break out from the Northern Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé, be the vanguard; Yúncháng, guard the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Qián, Mí Zhú, and I will be in the middle,\Nprotecting our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall obey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.58,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(102,344)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1135,1420)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled - Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Lord Xuándé, I assume\Nyou've been well since we last met?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come to seek shelter.\NI'm ashamed to ask it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what are you saying, Xuándé?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù is one of the most wicked men. \NHe won't achieve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I ought to punish him alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's banquet will help ease\Nyour pain from losing your land!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, Liú Bèi is one of \Nmany ambitious men in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}If we don't plan against him now,\Nwe will surely suffer later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Wénruò, you conceived both the 'two tigers competing for food'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and 'driving the tiger to devour the wolf' plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Both of them should've worked but failed.\NWeren't they all plans against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Now this tiger was defeated and has come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, you only need one phrase to eliminate Liú Bèi;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}why use strategies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Fèngxiào!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiào, Xún Yù advised me to kill Xuándé.\NWhat do you think about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi is ambitious too.\NIf he lives, isn't he going to stir trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, you formed a righteous army\Nto rid the people of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Only your integrity will lure prodigies;\Nthe lack thereof will repel them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Xuándé has made quite a name for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Now he has come to you in great peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}To kill him would be killing a virtuous man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Talents across the realm will be fearful\Nand will hesitate to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Who else would you rely on\Nto pacify the realm then, My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}You can eliminate one potentially dangerous person,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}but dash the hopes of all within the four seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, you can't be too rash;\Nyou must consider it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Sir, your words are what I truly think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I was just speaking in jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Very well. I will make a statement to the court tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}to recommend Liú Bèi as Governor of Yùzhōu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, do not do that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, do not recommend\NLiú Bèi to the throne at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Liú Bèi is a hero and holds lofty ambitions,\Nnever content to be a subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Giving him any land would be like caring for a tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}In the end, he won't stand being under other men;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}better to get rid of him forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}We should not dispose of this tiger,\Nlet alone eliminate him this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}This is an era where having heroes is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I can't lose the hearts of them just because I want to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Guō Fèngxiào's belief is the same I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Say no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 2nd year of the Jiàn'ān era\Nunder Emperor Xiàn,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,while Cáo Cāo joined forces\Nwith Liú Bèi to invade Lǚ Bù,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Xiù, with Liú Biǎo,\Nstationed troops at the City of Wǎn,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to attack Cáo Cāo and seize power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On one side, Cáo Cāo attacked Lǚ Bù;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other, he led a grand army through three different roads to punish Zhāng Xiù.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! Xiàhóu Dūn, vanguard of Cáo Cāo's army,\Nhas set up camp at Yùshuǐ!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Scout again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.42,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,361)\fade(255,0,255,0,540,1485,1740)}Jiǎ Xǔ\NStyled - Wénhé
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,General?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.26,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(90,293)\fade(255,0,255,0,535,1735,2100)}Zhāng Xiù
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo is a capable commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All civil officials and generals\Nunder his banner are experts in warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's leading 150,000 troops divided in three from three different directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a testament to his might.\NWe can't possibly face him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then according to your statement, Wénhé,\Nwhat do think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With your uncle dead and the\Ninsufficiency of Liú Biǎo's army,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in my modest opinion... the best course of action...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we might as well do him a favor and just surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you are saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it would be better to be\Nunder Cáo Cāo's banner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with my eyebrows low as a\Ndefeated enemy general?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That... this is a matter of time and might! A matter of time and might!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A matter of time and might?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Receive the official seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the way for my horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(102,355)\fade(255,0,255,0,575,1100,1380)}Diǎn Wéi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any beauties within this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yesterday at night,\Nthrough the side of the chambers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I saw a married woman, who looked very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After asking, they told me she was the wife of Zhāng Jì.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A very beautiful woman...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Zhāng Jì is the uncle of Zhāng Xiù.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, as he's recently\Nleft this world, I'm afraid—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Zhāng Xiù?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a defeated general.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if he gets mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he complain about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go. Take 50 armed men and bring them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,May I dare ask for your name, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the wife of Zhāng Jì, Lady Zōu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, have you've heard of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long heard of your name, General.\NI am fortunate to meet you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for you that I allowed\NZhāng Xiù to surrender and live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise the Zhāng clan\Nwould have been exterminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful, for I owe my\Nvery life to your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To finally meet you today, ma'am, is heaven's blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, are you willing\Nto sleep with me tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Being looked after by you, General, is the blessing of three lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you stay in the city for too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Xiù will have suspicions, and\NI fear outsiders will begin to gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommorow, you will go with me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and dwell in my camp outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I willing to suffer such a big disgrace?\NThis won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,General, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He kidnapped my aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one hide their feelings\Nand do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If Cáo Cāo flees the city, he will camp outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's his valiant general, Diǎn Wéi,\Nwho acts as his bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else may enter unless stated otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By restricting access from outside or inside,\Nthey can be on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you act rashly, the consequences\Nwill be extremely disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,General?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For this matter... you must heed my advice. \NMake sure not to leak it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In the following days, that\Nbastard will come out to discuss matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\}You need to do it like {\i1}this{\i0}, in {\i1}that{\i0} way...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,General, why have you called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hú Chē'er.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yesterday, Cáo Cāo called his\Nofficers to a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I ordered many of my soldiers\Nto desert en masse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With that excuse, I was able to camp\Nin the center of his camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know my plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:49.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,403)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1900,2180)}Hú Chē'er
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Though my plan to move troops\Nhasn't made Cáo Cāo suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a man guarding the tent in the camp, Diǎn Wéi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.44,0:24:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is very brave and fierce, and getting in will be most difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I summoned you to discuss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.75,0:24:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's fearsome about \NDiǎn Wéi is his twin halberds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Lord, invite him tomorrow to have some wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Assure he gets really drunk, then have him return. Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what? What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.06,0:24:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sneak into the tent and steal his halberds; no need to fear him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.60,0:24:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Enact your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you sure can handle large amounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:24:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.49,0:24:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.50,0:25:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.26,0:25:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get too drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.66,0:25:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very famous! It's rare to even see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.00,0:25:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this once, drink as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I must always be by my lord to protect him!
