Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.48,0:28:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord! My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.23,0:28:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son, Cáo Áng, and nephew, Cáo Ānmín...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.14,0:28:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we found their bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But General Diǎn Wéi...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.51,0:28:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,General Diǎn Wéi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.00,0:28:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.41,0:28:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Diǎn Wéi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.06,0:29:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.23,0:29:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.44,0:29:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,General Yú Jìn... he...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.21,0:29:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Yú Jìn?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.40,0:29:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yú Jìn took advantage and rebelled,\Nattacking Xiàhóu Dūn's Qīngzhōu regiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.80,0:29:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killed many of our men!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.55,0:29:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.94,0:29:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yú Jìn heard of my defeat,\Nhe did not come to rescue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.76,0:29:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, he took advantage and rebelled,\Nlike dropping stones on someone stuck in a well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.72,0:29:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight him with all I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.41,0:29:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.61,0:29:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.01,0:29:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yú Jìn led his troops to pursue Zhāng Xiù\Nfor more than 100 lǐ!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.54,0:29:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He won total victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.99,0:29:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We followed Yú Jìn, who pursued\NZhāng Xiù through several roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.12,0:30:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His strength is exhausted, and he found himself isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.55,0:30:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The defeated troops have fled to Liú Biǎo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.45,0:30:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.12,0:30:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yú Jìn,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.16,0:30:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Some fellows accused you\Nof excessive cruelty and rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.13,0:30:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, that—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.40,0:30:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.31,0:30:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Qīngzhōu army rebelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.88,0:30:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me first \Nbut fight them yourself instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.22,0:30:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They were coming rapidly;\Nthere was no time to report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.19,0:31:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, this affair was never General Yú Jìn's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.13,0:31:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It is mine; I was too laid back!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.69,0:31:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Qīngzhōu regiment took advantage and raided the countryside!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.44,0:31:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thereafter, Yú Jìn killed those curs,\Ncalming the people along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.31,0:31:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yú Jìn, when you saw me coming your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.15,0:31:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't explain your actions.\NInstead, you prepared for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.14,0:31:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.34,0:31:35.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(558,371)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,2300,2620)}Yú Jìn\NStyled - Wénzé
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.52,0:31:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The rebels were on us. If we didn't prepare,\Nhow could we have resisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.24,0:31:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't come to me to explain; did you not fear I'd wrong you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.62,0:31:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Explanations are trivial;\N defense is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.90,0:31:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.10,0:31:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,General, even under pressure,\Nyou were able to build a firm base.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.80,0:31:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You ignored slander and turned defeat into victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.28,0:31:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the famed generals of old...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.21,0:32:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,could hardly compare!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.08,0:32:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.15,0:32:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo not only lost his favorite general, Diǎn Wéi,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.55,0:32:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but also his beloved son and nephew, Cáo Áng and Cáo Ānmín.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.80,0:32:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Luckily, Yú Jìn and others did their best to aid him,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.52,0:32:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing Cáo Cāo to turn defeat into victory and danger into safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.79,0:32:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 3rd year of the Jiàn'ān era,\NYuán Shù proclaimed himself Emperor in Huáinán.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.80,0:32:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When he heard of it,\NCáo Cāo led an army of 170,000 troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,joining forces with Sūn Cè of Jiāngdōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.34,0:33:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi of Yùzhōu, and Lǚ Bù of Xúzhōu,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.10,0:33:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to attack Yuán Shù through three directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.31,0:33:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seeing himself surrounded by enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.12,0:33:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuán Shú was forced to sail across the Huái River,\Nbringing treasures with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.68,0:33:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He ordered Lǐ Fēng and others to\Ngarrison and defend Shòuchūn to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.19,0:33:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo was facing another enemy in a prolonged and bloody battle once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.89,0:34:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ask Rèn Jùn's subordinate, the supplies overseer, Wáng Hòu,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.27,0:34:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to come to my tent right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.10,0:34:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.85,0:34:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.05,0:34:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.22,0:34:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.27,0:34:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Out of those 400,000 hú of grain we borrowed from Sūn Cè,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.62,0:34:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,how much are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.97,0:34:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that much left.\NThere's barely enough to feed 170,000 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.34,0:35:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you need to reduce the rations
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.58,0:35:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for each soldier at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.05,0:35:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they complain, what to do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.43,0:35:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.80,0:35:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, even if we reduce the rations,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.18,0:35:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only enough for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.14,0:35:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.47,0:35:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.56,0:36:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.03,0:36:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.64,0:36:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.08,0:36:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.18,0:37:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who thought to reduce our rations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.11,0:37:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they taking our food?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.08,0:37:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.44,0:37:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.72,0:37:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose idea was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.56,0:37:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose idea was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.66,0:37:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.97,0:37:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.79,0:37:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.30,0:37:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord!\NLook what's happening out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.51,0:37:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}By reducing rations, the soldiers are rioting!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.66,0:37:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}They're saying that you've cheated them!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.22,0:37:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.45,0:37:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord! Think of a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.10,0:37:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Otherwise, they will all mutiny against us!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.00,0:38:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.70,0:38:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I was thinking of borrowing\None thing from you to calm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.84,0:38:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I hope you won't resent me for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.14,0:38:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}What 'resentment?'
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.50,0:38:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}What does My Lordship want to borrow from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.66,0:38:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.18,0:38:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I will borrow your head and expose it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.95,0:38:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.40,0:38:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.30,0:38:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I've done nothing wrong! How can you-
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.15,0:38:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I know that you're innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.58,0:38:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}but if I don't kill you, the army will mutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.70,0:38:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}After you die, your wife\Nand children shall be in my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.98,0:38:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}You need not worry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.70,0:39:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.28,0:39:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.40,0:39:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.89,0:39:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wáng Hòu knowingly distributed small rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.82,0:39:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime for withholding rations, according to military law, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.16,0:39:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,death!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.20,0:39:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.68,0:39:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was him, the supplies overseer?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserve death!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.29,0:40:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He deserves death! Kill him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.20,0:40:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, I will take my leave for the last time...
